    "8548123": {
      "title": "On the Briançon-Skoda theorem on a singular variety",
      "abstract": "Let $Z$ be a germ of a reduced analytic space of pure dimension. We provide an analytic proof of the uniform Briancon-Skoda theorem for the local ring $\\mathcal{O}_Z$; a result which was previously proved by Huneke by algebraic methods. For ideals with few generators we also get much sharper results."
